OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry. Then the rest of the
OL,7,Fnight will stay dry with variable
OL,8,Famounts of cloud. Patchy mist or fog
OL,9,Fand frost. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FA dry day with plenty of
OL,12,Fsunshine but eastern Aberdeenshire may
OL,13,Fsee some low cloud at first. Quite
OL,14,Fwarm inland but cooler along the east
OL,15,Fcoast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
