OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FRemaining
OL,6,Fdry and settled with plenty of
OL,7,Fsunshine, warm by afternoon inland.
OL,8,FPatchy overnight low cloud in the
OL,9,Feast. A touch of overnight frost
OL,10,Fpossible.
